{"tid":1585544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"影片推廣, 嫲嫲修道人叫我幫推既","createTime":"2019-09-21T15:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T16:30:47.000Z","uid":254555,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"26ca69c150823ee2c085c97b726f243b523f705e","tid":1585544,"uid":254555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"並非賣廣告, like唔like追唔追都唔關我事, 我只係聽自稱嫲嫲既老媽子命令上唻推俾前線睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LjBypvRnJZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLjBypvRnJZ4&d=zoPJ6Qh4RBVN8MuZ9mClYoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=b1aa4742\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LjBypvRnJZ4</a><br />\n<br />\n昨日已推過, 老媽叫我再推一次, 重點係1小時28分開始, 有前線可做之事<br />\n無時間睇哂或對玄學完全不信既唔駛理會前面內容<br />\n但想了解前文後理就由14分鐘開始睇<br />\n<br />\n自推10次, 有緣者見"},{"pid":"533873d5ff96b5ea155fcfa59c6acf5c0b6e154d","tid":1585544,"uid":254555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:54:15.000Z","msg":"自推一"},{"pid":"7f78056383ad4b25e28ef381bcc86015148b590a","tid":1585544,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:54:55.000Z","msg":"我愛香港 我要清潔18區連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585340</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2204e6d92e86b6d6ba65119111039191c7ade02b","tid":1585544,"uid":254555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"自推二"},{"pid":"2f2a2abd9bdc51cddadf037207426bfeeb33154d","tid":1585544,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"乖喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e942a77098e82f7b20f03335022401d0bff43939","tid":1585544,"uid":254555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f2a2abd9bdc51cddadf037207426bfeeb33154d","tid":1585544,"uid":282289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:57:06.000Z","msg":"乖喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf